<P>> I'm sure they will not just wipe the characters, you are

<BR>&gt; speculating and poorly so.
<P>I hope they don't ..
<P>&gt; The other players will suffer because those player who do not
<BR>&gt; want to play on the PVP server will crowd other servers. When a
<BR>&gt; server built to house 1500+ players houses 200, Verant starts to
<BR>&gt; lose money and other players would want to use that space for
<BR>&gt; regular servers. The server is not just something out there
<BR>&gt; floating on the net, it is an actual machine, and the PVP world
<BR>&gt; will occupy that machine. If it is not populated, the the other
<BR>&gt; machines are crowded, and that is who suffers.
<P>No, they will start with like 15 other servers, 1 mere PVP server doesn't make a difference.. if we were talking ...if they had 2 servers, and then yea, but 15:1 is nothing. (not exactly 15 but im sure they got like 10+ "rpg" servers)
